357
00:37:06,950 --> 00:37:07,670
The author is Fu Yunshen.

358
00:37:07,750 --> 00:37:08,990
He is your boyfriend, right?

359
00:37:10,190 --> 00:37:11,270
How do you know?

360
00:37:11,710 --> 00:37:12,950
Everybody knows.

361
00:37:13,030 --> 00:37:14,670
Every time he came here, he said,

362
00:37:14,990 --> 00:37:16,470
